Charts
Upon the release of Overexposed, due to strength of digital downloads, &quot;Wipe Your Eyes&quot; debuted at number 80 on the US Billboard Hot 100 for the issue dated July 14, 2012.20 After the release of the album, as a results of the downloads the song debuted on the South Korea Gaon International Chart at number 18 on June 24, 2012, with sales of 25,772 digital copies.21 The next week, it fell to number 23 and sold additional 11,876 copies.22 It stayed on the chart for total of four weeks.23



